data.description: This home is 1,712 square feet. This home has 4 bedrooms + 2 bathrooms, with a 2-car garage. It also features granite counter tops, Taexx Built-in Pest Control, post-tension slab, executive height vanities, two-toned paint, front yard landscaping, ceramic tile, hardwood cabinets, energy star and more! The owner suite has a beautiful full bathroom with a walk-in closet. The kitchen is open to the living room, perfect for entertaining. Photos and Video are of our Palo Verde plan. Interior packages may vary, speak with an Express Sales Representative for more information!
